    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) that defines the 'mint' standard. This chassis features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting perfectly calibrated individual throttle bodies and a recently overhauled VANOS system for peak variable valve timing performance. The subframe has been meticulously reinforced with a bespoke plate kit to ensure structural rigidity. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a M-Variable limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The suspension is upgraded with Bilstein PSS10 adjustable dampers, maintaining factory-plus geometry. Finished in Carbon Black with flawless Cinnamon Nappa leather, the factory clear coat remains deep and swirl-free. This is a turn-key, collector-quality machine with zero deferred maintenance.",
